    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第一人称合作射击游戏</strong>，融合了<strong>残酷、硬核、恐怖、掠夺、撤离</strong>等元素，<strong>程序生成</strong>与<strong>永久死亡机制</strong>贯穿其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏概述：</strong> 欢迎来到 <strong><i>Exile Protocol（流放协议）</i></strong>，一款令人心跳加速的科幻第一人称射击游戏，你和朋友将深入由程序生成的地下掩体，对抗无数噩梦般的怪物。在这个残酷的世界中，唯一目标就是生存，每一个决定都可能决定生死存亡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/9f42a9232b6b77e18b7b9de49188024f.avif?t=1760370394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras_big/9f42a9232b6b77e18b7b9de49188024f.avif?t=1760370394 width=800 height=128 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/e267d860ca47d4954af2cb35145bf3ab.poster.avif?t=1760370394\" width=750 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/e267d860ca47d4954af2cb35145bf3ab.webm?t=1760370394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>在线合作模式：</strong> 单人独闯或与好友组队协作，制定战略、应对挑战，提高生存几率，让每一次任务都成为难忘的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的队友一起，权衡风险与收益。是悄悄绕过潜伏的怪物去获取稀有武器，还是发动交火，明知枪声可能吸引更可怕的敌人？你搜集到的战利品不仅对当前生存至关重要，还能强化你们的技能与装备，助力未来的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/b8303553168ba8c784dc4839436e631f.avif?t=1760370394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras_big/b8303553168ba8c784dc4839436e631f.avif?t=1760370394 width=800 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/e8b3ce62608f5bce859074658ef841da.poster.avif?t=1760370394\" width=750 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/e8b3ce62608f5bce859074658ef841da.webm?t=1760370394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>多样怪物：</strong> 遭遇种类繁多的恐怖怪物，每种都有独特的强项与弱点。有的擅长听觉感知，有的被光吸引，还有的视觉敏锐。团队沟通至关重要，合理战术应对，识破其行为习性，方可有效生存与掠夺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/d65abb6e35de78067fdc6926d025b30a.avif?t=1760370394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras_big/d65abb6e35de78067fdc6926d025b30a.avif?t=1760370394 width=800 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/25297d9f1d1e863fec6a068e96857069.poster.avif?t=1760370394\" width=750 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/25297d9f1d1e863fec6a068e96857069.webm?t=1760370394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>装备自定义：</strong> 你可以自由组合多种武器、瞄具、弹匣、消音器与激光瞄准器，打造属于你的最佳战斗配置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/ea03caf2bd7cf81bd24afeb8d1c7f4c0.avif?t=1760370394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras_big/ea03caf2bd7cf81bd24afeb8d1c7f4c0.avif?t=1760370394 width=800 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/e1f7b3bf4b4e9341025e5822c0bda5bd.poster.avif?t=1760370394\" width=750 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/e1f7b3bf4b4e9341025e5822c0bda5bd.webm?t=1760370394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>动态战利品系统：</strong> 收集丰富的武器、装备和资源，强化你的角色，提升撤离成功率。每件装备都具备不同属性，如生命值、耐力、隐匿（声音抑制）、精准度与稳定性，适配你的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>其他特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>程序生成的掩体：</strong> 每次任务都是全新体验，地图结构、战利品与敌人位置皆随机变化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高压氛围体验：</strong> 恐怖音效与视觉设计相结合，令你在黑暗中前行时始终肾上腺素飙升。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>永久死亡机制：</strong> 在 <strong><i>Exile Protocol</i></strong> 中，一旦死亡即为终结。每次游戏都是全新挑战，角色一旦阵亡，便永远失去。这种高风险机制极大增强团队紧张感，每一个决定都至关重要。是冒险前行还是稳妥行事？决定权交给你，但后果必须承担。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏目标：</strong> 明确而危险——探索阴森掩体深处，搜集珍贵战利品，并安全撤离。协作是关键，但要保持警觉——每一个阴影中都可能潜伏猎杀者，每一丝声音都可能是末日的序曲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你与队友是否准备好面对 <i>Exile Protocol</i> 的恐惧了？掩体在等待，怪物在饥饿。你能幸存归来，还是只是失落名单中的又一人？选择权在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras/904ac92745bd7f559a3c4b7f369d2d3f.avif?t=1760370394\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235150/extras_big/904ac92745bd7f559a3c4b7f369d2d3f.avif?t=1760370394 width=800 height=128 /></span></p>",
